{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.1","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:1","prev_osis_id":"Matt.023.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La destruction de J\u00e9rusalem et l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Fils de l\u2019homme<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. (Mc 13:1-13. Lu 21:5-19.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Comme J\u00e9sus s\u2019en allait, au sortir du temple, ses disciples s\u2019approch\u00e8rent pour lui en faire remarquer les constructions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.2","name":"Matthieu 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.23.39","name":"Matthieu 23:39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.23.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.2","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:2","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Mais il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Voyez-vous tout cela? Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">il ne restera pas ici pierre sur pierre qui ne soit renvers\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.3","name":"Matthieu 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.1","name":"Matthieu 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.3","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:3","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il s\u2019assit sur la montagne des oliviers. Et les disciples vinrent en particulier lui faire cette question: Dis-nous, quand cela arrivera-t-il, et quel sera le signe de ton av\u00e8nement et de la fin du monde?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.4","name":"Matthieu 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.2","name":"Matthieu 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.4","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:4","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>J\u00e9sus leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Prenez garde que personne ne vous s\u00e9duise.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.5","name":"Matthieu 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.3","name":"Matthieu 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.5","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:5","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car plusieurs viendront sous mon nom, disant: C\u2019est moi qui suis le Christ. Et ils s\u00e9duiront beaucoup de gens.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.6","name":"Matthieu 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.4","name":"Matthieu 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.6","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:6","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Vous entendrez parler de guerres et de bruits de guerres: gardez-vous d\u2019\u00eatre troubl\u00e9s, car il faut que ces choses arrivent. Mais ce ne sera pas encore la fin.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.7","name":"Matthieu 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.5","name":"Matthieu 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.7","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:7","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Une nation s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera contre une nation, et un royaume contre un royaume, et il y aura, en divers lieux, des famines et des tremblements de terre.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.8","name":"Matthieu 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.6","name":"Matthieu 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.8","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:8","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Tout cela ne sera que le commencement des douleurs.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.9","name":"Matthieu 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.7","name":"Matthieu 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.9","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:9","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors on vous livrera aux tourments, et l\u2019on vous fera mourir; et vous serez ha\u00efs de toutes les nations, \u00e0 cause de mon nom.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.10","name":"Matthieu 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.8","name":"Matthieu 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.10","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:10","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors aussi plusieurs succomberont, et ils se trahiront, se ha\u00efront les uns les autres.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.11","name":"Matthieu 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.9","name":"Matthieu 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.11","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:11","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Plusieurs faux proph\u00e8tes s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8veront, et ils s\u00e9duiront beaucoup de gens.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.12","name":"Matthieu 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.10","name":"Matthieu 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.12","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:12","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">parce que l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 se sera accrue, la charit\u00e9 du plus grand nombre se refroidira.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.13","name":"Matthieu 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.11","name":"Matthieu 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.13","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:13","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais celui qui pers\u00e9v\u00e9rera jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la fin sera sauv\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.14","name":"Matthieu 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.12","name":"Matthieu 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.14","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:14","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Cette bonne nouvelle du royaume sera pr\u00each\u00e9e dans le monde entier, pour servir de t\u00e9moignage \u00e0 toutes les nations. Alors viendra la fin.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.15","name":"Matthieu 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.13","name":"Matthieu 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.15","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:15","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-35: cf. (Mc 13:14-31. Lu 21:20-33; 17:22-25, 31, 37.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi, lorsque vous verrez l\u2019abomination de la d\u00e9solation, dont a parl\u00e9 le proph\u00e8te<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Daniel, \u00e9tablie en lieu saint, que celui qui lit fasse attention!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.16","name":"Matthieu 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.14","name":"Matthieu 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.16","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:16","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">alors, que ceux qui seront en Jud\u00e9e fuient dans les montagnes;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.17","name":"Matthieu 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.15","name":"Matthieu 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.17","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:17","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">que celui qui sera sur le toit ne descende pas pour prendre ce qui est dans sa maison;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.18","name":"Matthieu 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.16","name":"Matthieu 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.18","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:18","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et que celui qui sera dans les champs ne retourne pas en arri\u00e8re pour prendre son manteau.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.19","name":"Matthieu 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.17","name":"Matthieu 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.19","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:19","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Malheur aux femmes qui seront enceintes et \u00e0 celles qui allaiteront en ces jours-l\u00e0!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.20","name":"Matthieu 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.18","name":"Matthieu 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.20","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:20","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Priez pour que votre fuite n\u2019arrive pas en hiver, ni un jour de<\/span><span class=\"wj\">sabbat.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.21","name":"Matthieu 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.19","name":"Matthieu 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.21","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:21","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car alors, la d\u00e9tresse sera si grande qu\u2019il n\u2019y en a point eu de pareille depuis le commencement du monde jusqu\u2019\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent, et qu\u2019il n\u2019y en aura jamais.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.22","name":"Matthieu 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.20","name":"Matthieu 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.22","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:22","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et, si ces jours n\u2019\u00e9taient abr\u00e9g\u00e9s, personne ne serait sauv\u00e9; mais, \u00e0 cause des \u00e9lus, ces jours seront abr\u00e9g\u00e9s.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.23","name":"Matthieu 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.21","name":"Matthieu 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.23","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:23","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si quelqu\u2019un vous dit alors:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Le Christ est ici, ou: Il est l\u00e0, ne le croyez pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.24","name":"Matthieu 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.22","name":"Matthieu 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.24","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:24","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car il s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8vera de faux Christs et de faux proph\u00e8tes; ils feront de grands prodiges et des miracles, au point de s\u00e9duire, s\u2019il \u00e9tait possible, m\u00eame les \u00e9lus.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.25","name":"Matthieu 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.23","name":"Matthieu 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.25","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:25","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Voici, je vous l\u2019ai annonc\u00e9 d\u2019avance.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.26","name":"Matthieu 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.24","name":"Matthieu 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.26","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:26","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si donc on vous dit: Voici, il est dans le d\u00e9sert, n\u2019y allez pas; voici, il est dans les chambres, ne le croyez pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.27","name":"Matthieu 24:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.25","name":"Matthieu 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.27","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:27","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car, comme l\u2019\u00e9clair part de l\u2019orient et se montre jusqu\u2019en occident, ainsi sera l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Fils de l\u2019homme.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.28","name":"Matthieu 24:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.26","name":"Matthieu 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.28","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:28","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">En quelque lieu que soit le cadavre, l\u00e0 s\u2019assembleront les aigles.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.29","name":"Matthieu 24:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.27","name":"Matthieu 24:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.29","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:29","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Aussit\u00f4t apr\u00e8s ces jours de d\u00e9tresse, le soleil s\u2019obscurcira, la lune ne donnera plus sa lumi\u00e8re, les \u00e9toiles tomberont du ciel, et les puissances des cieux seront \u00e9branl\u00e9es.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.30","name":"Matthieu 24:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.28","name":"Matthieu 24:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.30","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:30","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors le signe du Fils de l\u2019homme para\u00eetra dans le ciel, toutes les tribus de la terre<\/span><span class=\"wj\">se lamenteront, et elles verront le Fils de l\u2019homme venant sur les nu\u00e9es du ciel avec puissance et une grande gloire.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.31","name":"Matthieu 24:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.29","name":"Matthieu 24:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.31","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:31","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il enverra ses anges avec<\/span><span class=\"wj\">la trompette retentissante, et ils rassembleront ses \u00e9lus des quatre vents, depuis une extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 des cieux jusqu\u2019\u00e0 l\u2019autre.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.32","name":"Matthieu 24:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.30","name":"Matthieu 24:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.32","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:32","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Instruisez-vous par une comparaison tir\u00e9e du figuier. D\u00e8s que ses branches deviennent tendres, et que les feuilles poussent, vous connaissez que l\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9 est proche.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.33","name":"Matthieu 24:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.31","name":"Matthieu 24:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.33","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:33","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">De m\u00eame, quand vous verrez toutes ces choses, sachez que le Fils de l\u2019homme est proche, \u00e0 la porte.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.34","name":"Matthieu 24:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.32","name":"Matthieu 24:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.34","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:34","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, cette g\u00e9n\u00e9ration ne passera point, que tout cela n\u2019arrive.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.35","name":"Matthieu 24:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.33","name":"Matthieu 24:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.35","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:35","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le ciel et la terre passeront, mais mes paroles ne passeront point.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.36","name":"Matthieu 24:36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.34","name":"Matthieu 24:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.36","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:36","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.037,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 la vigilance<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 36-51: cf. (Mc 13:32-37. Lu 21:34-36; 17:26-30, 34-36.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Pour ce qui est du jour et de l\u2019heure, personne ne le sait, ni les anges des cieux, ni le Fils, mais le P\u00e8re seul.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.37","name":"Matthieu 24:37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.35","name":"Matthieu 24:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.37","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:37","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ce qui arriva du temps de No\u00e9 arrivera de m\u00eame \u00e0 l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Fils de l\u2019homme.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.38","name":"Matthieu 24:38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.36","name":"Matthieu 24:36","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.38","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:38","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car, dans les jours qui pr\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e8rent le d\u00e9luge, les hommes mangeaient et buvaient, se mariaient et mariaient leurs enfants,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">jusqu\u2019au jour o\u00f9 No\u00e9 entra dans l\u2019arche;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.39","name":"Matthieu 24:39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.37","name":"Matthieu 24:37","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.39","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:39","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et ils ne se dout\u00e8rent de rien, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que le d\u00e9luge v\u00eent et les emport\u00e2t tous: il en sera de m\u00eame \u00e0 l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Fils de l\u2019homme.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.40","name":"Matthieu 24:40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.38","name":"Matthieu 24:38","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.40","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:40","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors, de deux hommes qui seront dans un champ, l\u2019un sera pris et l\u2019autre laiss\u00e9;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.41","name":"Matthieu 24:41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.39","name":"Matthieu 24:39","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.41","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:41","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">de deux femmes qui moudront \u00e0 la meule, l\u2019une sera prise et l\u2019autre laiss\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.42","name":"Matthieu 24:42","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.40","name":"Matthieu 24:40","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.42","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:42","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Veillez donc, puisque vous ne savez pas quel jour votre Seigneur viendra.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.43","name":"Matthieu 24:43","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.41","name":"Matthieu 24:41","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.43","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:43","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Sachez-le bien, si le ma\u00eetre de la maison savait \u00e0 quelle veille de la nuit le voleur doit venir, il veillerait et ne laisserait pas percer sa maison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.44","name":"Matthieu 24:44","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.42","name":"Matthieu 24:42","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.44","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:44","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi, vous aussi, tenez-vous pr\u00eats, car le Fils de l\u2019homme viendra \u00e0 l\u2019heure o\u00f9 vous n\u2019y penserez pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.45","name":"Matthieu 24:45","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.43","name":"Matthieu 24:43","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.45","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:45","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quel est donc le serviteur fid\u00e8le et prudent, que son ma\u00eetre a \u00e9tabli sur ses gens, pour leur donner la nourriture au temps convenable?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.46","name":"Matthieu 24:46","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.44","name":"Matthieu 24:44","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.46","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:46","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Heureux ce serviteur, que son ma\u00eetre, \u00e0 son arriv\u00e9e, trouvera faisant ainsi!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.47","name":"Matthieu 24:47","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.45","name":"Matthieu 24:45","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.47","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:47","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il l\u2019\u00e9tablira sur tous ses biens.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.48","name":"Matthieu 24:48","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.46","name":"Matthieu 24:46","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.48","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:48","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais, si c\u2019est un m\u00e9chant serviteur, qui dise en lui-m\u00eame: Mon ma\u00eetre tarde \u00e0 venir,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.49","name":"Matthieu 24:49","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.47","name":"Matthieu 24:47","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.49","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:49","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">s\u2019il se met \u00e0 battre ses compagnons, s\u2019il mange et boit avec les ivrognes,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.50","name":"Matthieu 24:50","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.48","name":"Matthieu 24:48","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.50","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:50","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.024.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">le ma\u00eetre de ce serviteur viendra le jour o\u00f9 il ne s\u2019y attend pas et \u00e0 l\u2019heure qu\u2019il ne conna\u00eet pas,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.51","name":"Matthieu 24:51","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.49","name":"Matthieu 24:49","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.51","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 24:51","prev_osis_id":"Matt.024.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.025.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.24.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">il le mettra en pi\u00e8ces, et lui donnera sa part avec les hypocrites:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">c\u2019est l\u00e0 qu\u2019il y aura des pleurs et des grincements de dents.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.24","name":"Matthieu 24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.25.1","name":"Matthieu 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.25.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.24.50","name":"Matthieu 24:50","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.24.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb6908e47.19669819');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb6908e47.19669819\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb6908e47.19669819","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb6908e47.19669819'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af8